text: Kathleen Stark (born 9 September 1975) is a German gymnast. She competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rostock
